In a bid to find Finn a suitable donor the â€˜Save Finn McEwanâ€™ campaign was launched. Finn, a massive Evertonian, was invited into Finch Farm to meet the Everton players to help raise awareness of the campaign back in March 2015 (see video below).
After Finnâ€™s regular clinic appointment at the Manchester Childrenâ€™s Hospital this morning Finn and his family received the news they had been praying for. Professor Rob Wynn told Finn that as far as he was concerned his â€œleukemia is cured, and the other serious conditions following the transplant were resolved.â€
